metadata.name: Rock Fauna
metadata.description:
Rust reds mix with sunshine yellows & other subdued hues to create an abstract-ly message.  The first in line in the TWU collection, 'Rock Fauna’ is a moment frozen in time, memorialized on the Ethereum Blockchain forever.  (00101.00000)

‘Artistic Redaction’ is the systematic deletion of words & emotion with the use of art. A way to move through the negative energy & find room for something new. TWU is a 2-Volume Series totaling 100 unique 1/1 ERC721 NFTs on the Ethereum Blockchain. Manifold contract / Metadata frozen on Arweave 

◉  TWU : Volume I, 1: 50 

◉  KSR: Png . 6600 x 6600 pixels . 300 ppi
